ood work!&#8221;<\/p><\/div><h4 class=\"tfree-client-name\">Hannah McHugh<\/h4><div class=\"tfree-client-designation\">PhD Scholar at School of Public Policy, University College of London<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free-item\"><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free\"><div class=\"sp-tfree-client-image\"><img width=\"120\" height=\"120\" src=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/pp-120x120.jpeg\" class=\"tfree-client-image wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/pp-120x120.jpeg 120w, http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/pp-300x300.jpeg 300w, http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/pp-150x150.jpeg 150w, http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/pp.jpeg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 120px) 100vw, 120px\" \/><\/div><div class=\"tfree-client-testimonial\"><p class=\"tfree-testimonial-content\"><p>&#8220;<strong>WISER WORLD<\/strong> provides in-depth &amp; concise analyses on relevant and important issues and challenges facing the diplomatic and international community. The wide range of perspectives on the various topics makes it very interesting! Kudos to the writers and the extraordinary team of<strong> WISER WORLD<\/strong>\u00a0for bringing out fresh and insightful bouquet of reflective commentaries.&#8221;<\/p>\n<\/p><\/div><h4 class=\"tfree-client-name\">Dr Parama Sinha Palit <\/h4><div class=\"tfree-client-designation\">Adjunct Senior Fellow with RSIS, Singapore<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free-item\"><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free\"><div class=\"sp-tfree-client-image\"><img width=\"120\" height=\"120\" src=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/img_20200813_213154-1-120x120.jpg\" class=\"tfree-client-image wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/img_20200813_213154-1-120x120.jpg 120w, http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/img_20200813_213154-1-150x150.jpg 150w, http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/img_20200813_213154-1.jpg 250w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 120px) 100vw, 120px\" \/><\/div><div class=\"tfree-client-testimonial\"><p class=\"tfree-testimonial-content\"><p>&#8220;Thank you Wiser World for giving me this opportunity. I really had a great experience. This work experience really helped me to learn about various things such as how to do research work and also about different psychological disorders.&#8221;<\/p>\n<\/p><\/div><h4 class=\"tfree-client-name\">Ishita Bansal<\/h4><div class=\"tfree-client-designation\">B.A. Psychology, Wilson College, Mumbai<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free-item\"><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free\"><div class=\"sp-tfree-client-image\"><img width=\"120\" height=\"120\" src=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Lakshya-120x120.png\" class=\"tfree-client-image wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Lakshya-120x120.png 120w, http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Lakshya-150x150.png 150w, http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Lakshya.png 250w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 120px) 100vw, 120px\" \/><\/div><div class=\"tfree-client-testimonial\"><p class=\"tfree-testimonial-content\"><p>&#8220;&#8230;was really a great working experience with Wiser World and especially with the team\/mentors. Looking forward to working with you again in the future&#8221;<\/p>\n<\/p><\/div><h4 class=\"tfree-client-name\">Lakshya Pokharna<\/h4><div class=\"tfree-client-designation\">B.Tech. Electronics and Communications, BIT Mesra<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free-item\"><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free\"><div class=\"sp-tfree-client-image\"><img width=\"120\" height=\"120\" src=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/20200712_130028-1-120x120.jpg\" class=\"tfree-client-image wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/20200712_130028-1-120x120.jpg 120w, http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/20200712_130028-1-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 120px) 100vw, 120px\" \/><\/div><div class=\"tfree-client-testimonial\"><p class=\"tfree-testimonial-content\"><p>&#8220;My experience in working for Wiser World was great, and it was made even better by my mentor who made it possible for me to better my writing skills. The whole expression made me more knowledgeable, and helped me further my skills.&#8221;<\/p>\n<\/p><\/div><h4 class=\"tfree-client-name\">Atlanta Choudhury<\/h4><div class=\"tfree-client-designation\">B.A. History (Hons), Delhi University<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free-item\"><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free\"><div class=\"sp-tfree-client-image\"><img width=\"120\" height=\"120\" src=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/img-20200616-wa0013-120x120.jpg\" class=\"tfree-client-image wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/img-20200616-wa0013-120x120.jpg 120w, http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/img-20200616-wa0013-150x150.jpg 150w, http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/img-20200616-wa0013.jpg 250w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 120px) 100vw, 120px\" \/><\/div><div class=\"tfree-client-testimonial\"><p class=\"tfree-testimonial-content\"><p>&#8220;My experience at Wiser World has been extremely beneficial and enjoyable for me. It has given me an outlet to write about topics that I am truly passionate about, nurtured my flair for writing, and has helped me articulate my knowledge of them&#8230;.&#8221;<\/p>\n<\/p><\/div><h4 class=\"tfree-client-name\">Annanya Guha<\/h4><div class=\"tfree-client-designation\">Former Intern<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free-item\"><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free\"><div class=\"sp-tfree-client-image\"><img width=\"120\" height=\"120\" src=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/20200722_092508-120x120.jpg\" class=\"tfree-client-image wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/20200722_092508-120x120.jpg 120w, http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/20200722_092508-150x150.jpg 150w, http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/20200722_092508.jpg 250w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 120px) 100vw, 120px\" \/><\/div><div class=\"tfree-client-testimonial\"><p class=\"tfree-testimonial-content\"><p>&#8220;&#8230;.I was allowed to choose any topic I wanted and that really helped me explore topics that I would not be able to otherwise. I was also helped by my mentor as he helped me understand the criteria the articles need to meet, things I can include in my article which would be relevant to the current times etc. I could write about things that would not be allowed conventionally and hence I am quite happy&#8221;<\/p>\n<\/p><\/div><h4 class=\"tfree-client-name\">Madhusree Dasgupta<\/h4><div class=\"tfree-client-designation\">B.A. Psychology, Loreto College, Calcutta University<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free-item\"><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free\"><div class=\"sp-tfree-client-image\"><img width=\"120\" height=\"120\" src=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/img_9298-1-120x120.jpg\" class=\"tfree-client-image wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/img_9298-1-120x120.jpg 120w, http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/img_9298-1-150x150.jpg 150w, http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/img_9298-1.jpg 250w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 120px) 100vw, 120px\" \/><\/div><div class=\"tfree-client-testimonial\"><p class=\"tfree-testimonial-content\"><p>&#8220;&#8230;indeed a great experience for me, I gained knowledge about writing, reading and being impartial while doing so. The platform provided by you to publish my articles boosted my confidence and I\u2019m glad for that.&#8221;<\/p>\n<\/p><\/div><h4 class=\"tfree-client-name\">Vaishali Jeswani<\/h4><div class=\"tfree-client-designation\">Hidayatullah National Law University, Raipur<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free-item\"><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free\"><div class=\"sp-tfree-client-image\"><img width=\"120\" height=\"120\" src=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/img-20200715-wa0000-120x120.jpg\" class=\"tfree-client-image wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/img-20200715-wa0000-120x120.jpg 120w, http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/img-20200715-wa0000-150x150.jpg 150w, http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/img-20200715-wa0000.jpg 250w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 120px) 100vw, 120px\" \/><\/div><div class=\"tfree-client-testimonial\"><p class=\"tfree-testimonial-content\"><p>&#8220;&#8230;had a great time working as a research intern. This work experience has really helped evolve my research and writing skills and I am thankful to the Wiser World team for giving me the opportunity to be a part of this great initiative.&#8221;<\/p>\n<\/p><\/div><h4 class=\"tfree-client-name\">Soumili Basu<\/h4><div class=\"tfree-client-designation\">B.A. Economics, Loreto College, Calcutta University<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free-item\"><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free\"><div class=\"sp-tfree-client-image\"><img width=\"120\" height=\"120\" src=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/0-120x120.jpeg\" class=\"tfree-client-image wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/0-120x12