Sukeerat Kaur Channi<\/h4><div class=\"tfree-client-designation\">B.A. Political Science, University of Delhi<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free-item\"><div class=\"sp-testimonial-free\"><div class=\"sp-tfree-client-image\"><img width=\"120\" height=\"120\" src=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/photo-120x120.jpeg\" class=\"tfree-client-image wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/photo-120x120.jpeg 120w, http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/photo-150x150.jpeg 150w, http:\/\/www.wiserworld.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/photo.jpeg 249w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 120px) 100vw, 120px\" \/><\/div><div class=\"tfree-client-testimonial\"><p class=\"tfree-testimonial-content\"><p>&#8220;&#8230;great and really learning experience working with your team. I was always helped during the internship, notified about my mistakes and appreciated for my work.&#8221;<\/p>\n<\/p><\/div><h4 class=\"tfree-client-name\">Vidhupriya Pandit<\/h4><div class=\"tfree-client-designation\">Former Intern<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><script type=\"application\/ld+json\">\n{\n  \"@context\": \"http:\/\/schema.org\",\n  \"@type\": \"Product\",\n  \"aggregateRating\": {\n    \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n    \"ratingValue\": \"0\",\n    \"reviewCount\": \"14\"\n  },\n  \"name\": \"Reviewers\",\n  \"review\": [{\n                \"@type\": \"Review\",\n                \"author\": \"Hannah McHugh\",\n                \"datePublished\": \"September 13, 2020\",\"description\": \"&quot;I am impressed by the in-depth coverage of various geo-strategic and geo-economic aspects. Hearty Congratulations to the team of WISER WORLD\u00a0for the platform. Keep up the good work!&quot;\",\"reviewRating\": {\n                  \"@type\": \"Rating\",\n                  \"bestRating\": \"5\",\n                  \"ratingValue\": \"\",\n                  \"worstRating\": \"1\"\n      